item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Network_ContentDelivery_OriginPull_Mapping
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Network_ContentDelivery_OriginPull_Mapping Datatype Description SoftLayer’s CDN allows for multiple origin pull domains and CNAME records. This container holds the origin pull configuration details. CDN currently supports origin pull method for HTTP content. Local cname The CNAME record. Type: string id The unique identifier of an origin pull configuration Type: string isSecureContent This indicates if an origin pull mapping is for the secure content or not.
